        "action": "Codify the UK Constitution into a single document following public consultation",
        "additional_details": "This new Constitution should have full legal force to protect against power imbalances and overruling of fundamental rights.",
        "background": "The UK Constitution is one of the few uncodified Constitutions in the world. Following a public consultation to hear their views, the Government should bring together all relevant laws and conventions into a single, codified Constitution. ",
